data.description: Welcome to Rio Vista in the master planned community of Mountains Edge! As you enter this neighborhood you will find tree lined streets leading to this wonderful 5 bedroom 3 bath home.  Attractive brick facade and a large covered porch greet you as you enter the home.  Downstairs features a thoughtfully designed kitchen with granite counter tops, stainless appliances, and windows overlooking the backyard.  The living room is spacious enough for all you gatherings and is open to the dining room.  Downstairs also includes a bedroom with a full bathroom that would be perfect as an guest suite.  Upstairs are four more bedrooms including the large primary suite with walk in closets and dual sink vanity in the bathroom.  The low maintenance backyard designed for relaxing with a large patio and synthetic grass.  Call for details!
